Output docs/cli-tree.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1300
Set Height 480
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

Hide
Type "cd /Volumes/Projects/mincut-context"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "mcx pack 'submission handler' --repo /Volumes/Projects/forms/wp-content/plugins/fluentform --budget 2500 --cache --format tree --exclude tests/** vendor/** node_modules/**"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 7s
